text: Feelings () is a 1968 Lithuanian drama movie directed by Algirdas Dausa and Almantas Grikevičius. It stars Regimantas Adomaitis, Juozas Budraitis, Algimantas Masiulis, Vytautas Paukštė. ==Other websites== * Category:1968 drama movies Category:Lithuanian movies Category:Movies set in Lithuania
